                        <div class="post__body" analytics>
                                <div class="u-mb">

                                    <img class="imagezoom__img" src="https://loveincorporated.blob.core.windows.net/contentimages/main/ee13ec0b-d60e-476e-8ff6-7ea0615aa10f-butterscotch-pecan--shortbread-recipe-bake-of.jpg" alt="Butterscotch and pecan shortbread biscuits recipe">

                                </div>

                            <p>Just the thing for enjoying as a mid-afternoon treat &ndash; and the ideal way to celebrate the return of <em>The Great British Bake Off </em>&ndash; these butterscotch and pecan shortbread biscuits have a delicate, melt-in-the-mouth texture and buttery richness that makes them pretty much irresistible.</p>

<p>The recipe comes from the newly released cookbook, <em>The Great British Bake Off: Comfort Bakes, </em>which features a delicious array of sweet and savoury recipes from Paul Hollywood, Prue Leith and the 2024 bakers.</p>

<p>In creating this recipe, it&#39;s clear the team have put their expertise to good use &ndash; the flecks of butterscotch and pecan threaded through the shortbread add tiny pockets of sweetness and a lovely nutty crunch. We think these beauties are best served with a cup of tea, for the ultimate dunking experience.</p>

<p><em>For US ingredients and measurements, use the drop-down menu and select &lsquo;Cups&rsquo;.</em></p>


                            <div class="layout">

                                <div class="layout__item u-1/2-lap">

                                    <h3 class="heading heading--delta">Ingredients</h3>

                                    <div class="u-pb- u-pl">
                                        <select id="ingredients-select" class="u-1/1" name="weight-conversion">
                                            <option value="0">Metric</option>
                                            <option value="1">Cups</option>
                                            <option value="2">Imperial</option>
                                        </select>
                                    </div>

                                        <ul name="ingredients-metric">
                                                <li>85 g butterscotch candies</li>
                                                <li>50 g pecans</li>
                                                <li>200 g unsalted butter, softened</li>
                                                <li>100 g caster sugar, plus extra for sprinkling</li>
                                                <li>1 tsp vanilla paste</li>
                                                <li>250 g plain flour, plus extra for dusting</li>
                                                <li>25 g cornflour</li>
                                                <li>25 g rice flour</li>
                                                <li>0.5 tsp baking powder</li>
                                                <li>0.5 tsp fine salt</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul name="ingredients-imperial" class="u-visuallyhidden">
                                                <li>3 oz butterscotch candies</li>
                                                <li>1.8 oz pecans</li>
                                                <li>7.1 oz unsalted butter, softened</li>
                                                <li>3.5 oz caster sugar, plus extra for sprinkling</li>
                                                <li>1 tsp vanilla paste</li>
                                                <li>8.8 oz plain flour, plus extra for dusting</li>
                                                <li>0.9 oz cornflour</li>
                                                <li>0.9 oz rice flour</li>
                                                <li>0.5 tsp baking powder</li>
                                                <li>0.5 tsp fine salt</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul name="ingredients-cups" class="u-visuallyhidden">
                                                <li>3 oz butterscotch candies</li>
                                                <li>1.8 oz pecans</li>
                                                <li>7.1 oz unsalted butter, softened</li>
                                                <li>3.5 oz superfine sugar, plus extra for sprinkling</li>
                                                <li>1 tsp vanilla paste</li>
                                                <li>8.8 oz all-purpose flour, plus extra for dusting</li>
                                                <li>0.9 oz cornstarch</li>
                                                <li>0.9 oz rice flour</li>
                                                <li>0.5 tsp baking powder</li>
                                                <li>0.5 tsp fine salt</li>
                                        </ul>
